In re Resignation of Tankersley.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Tankersley (1991), 61 Ohio St.3d 1204.]

(No. 91-1427 Submitted July 31, 1991 Decided August 7, 1991.)

The resignation of Hugh R. Tankersley as an attorney, Registration No. 0009404, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
